                <div class="col-lg-12 text-center py-3">
                    <div class="info-message">
                        Please Log In or Register to View or Create: an Event, Bring a Dish, Schedule a Meal, or Deliver a Meal. 
                        Thank you.
                    </div>
                </div>                
